title: FireVine 1.2 -- vinefire.com bot --
description:
--==FireVine==--
Created by Dave Harold

--==About==--
This program will automatically add your desired urls to the site VineFire.com every 60+ seconds, in a hidden Internet Explorer window. Minimize sit back, relax, and watch the clicks/money roll in.

--==Setup==--
1. Enter the desired titles, and urls into the FireVine.ini file, if you need more just keep the naming/numbering style the same.  "title1" matches "url1"
2. Enter the number of links you have setup in your FireVine.ini.
3. Enter the the time you wish to wait, in seconds, between adding links. Minimum delay is set to 60 seconds.
5. When you have setup your FireVine.ini file, run FireVine.exe

**NOTE**
I have seen some links take up to 8 minutes to appear on the main page. Be patient.


--==Disclaimer==--
Use this program at your own risk, I will not be held responsible for anything. If you have any questions, comments, or suggestions you can direct them to me on the forums.

--==History==--
v1.2
  *Added update feature, I don't know why I didn't add it before.
  *Hopefully fixed a crash error.

v1.1
  *Fixed links not posting, thank you vinefire for changing the forms.
  *Added error logging.
  *Made some other minor improvements.

v1.0
  *First public release.



Remember the newest version can always be found at http://youbot.nl.eu.org along with all previous version.
